&lt;p&gt;We’re hiring a Content Editor to support DZone’s editorial and contributor operations across both site and commercial content programs.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This role is ideal for someone who combines strong editorial instincts with technical curiosity and excellent organizational skills. You will help manage and publish technical content for DZone’s developer audience while also coordinating contributor-driven commercial projects from kickoff through completion.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;You will work closely with editorial, audience, sales, and contributor stakeholders to ensure content is accurate, engaging, timely, and aligned with DZone’s standards.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This requires excellent copyediting skills, strong project management abilities, comfort working with technical subject matter, and the ability to balance multiple priorities in a fast-moving publishing environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Employment Level:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; Mid-level&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
