&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Select, copyedit, and prepare technical site content for publication on DZone.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research trends in the SDLC and stay up to date with the latest innovations to support article planning, content strategies, newsletters, and community initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update site pages daily with fresh content and help ensure published content is timely, relevant, and aligned with editorial standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor support and editor inboxes, answer inquiries, delete spam, and escalate issues to the appropriate departments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with appropriate stakeholders to suggest site articles, community content, and other relevant editorial content to be featured in newsletters.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain relationships with contributors, authors, and community members.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support community-focused editorial initiatives, contributor engagement, and other programming that strengthen the DZone audience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with other team projects and initiatives as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
