&lt;p&gt;TechnologyAdvice is looking for an &lt;strong&gt;Email Marketing Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to help grow, engage, and optimize our newsletter audience across a portfolio of B2B media brands.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role sits within the Audience Development team and supports a newsletter ecosystem that includes 50+ newsletters and more than 3 million subscribers across multiple brands. You will help build lifecycle programs, improve subscriber engagement, support audience growth, and turn email performance data into clear recommendations that strengthen our newsletter strategy and monetization opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a hands-on role for someone who has managed email programs at a meaningful scale and can think beyond individual sends. The right person understands how to build segmented lifecycle journeys, test and improve engagement, and use tools, data, and AI thoughtfully to improve speed, quality, and performance.&lt;/p&gt;
