&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and optimize subscriber acquisition, engagement, retention, reactivation, and win-back programs across multiple newsletter audiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop lifecycle email journeys for different subscriber cohorts, brands, and audience segments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor newsletter and lifecycle performance, identify trends, and recommend ways to improve engagement, retention, and revenue opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and refine segmentation, personalization, behavioral targeting, and A/B testing strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with editorial, audience, marketing, AdOps, and executive stakeholders to align email programs with brand standards, audience needs, and business goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support newsletter monetization by helping evaluate sponsorship performance, audience engagement, and campaign opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use generative AI and AI-powered marketing tools to accelerate campaign planning, testing, analysis, reporting, and workflow efficiency while maintaining editorial judgment and quality standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate AI-generated outputs for accuracy, brand alignment, compliance, and audience relevance before they are used in subscriber-facing work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Present email performance insights and recommendations clearly to stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
